    <item>
      <title>Rules</title>
      <link>http://tod.npf.io/rules/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Sep 2014 14:55:32 EDT</pubDate>
      <author>Nate Finch</author>
      <guid>http://tod.npf.io/rules/</guid>
      <description>

&lt;h2 id=&#34;toc_0&#34;&gt;Character Generation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4d6, drop the lowest 6 times.  If you don&amp;rsquo;t like your scores, you can use the default array (15 14 13 12 10 8).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t be evil.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;toc_1&#34;&gt;Optional Rules&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We will be using feats.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Humans may take the variant abilities: +1 to two stats and a feat at first level.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;toc_2&#34;&gt;House Rules&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;None, so far.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
